bomberlandLandingPage.headline: <1>An open challenge for </1> machine learning
bomberlandLandingPage.bomberlandDescription: Bomberland is a multi-agent AI competition inspired by Bomberman.
bomberlandLandingPage.environmentGoal: Program intelligent agents using strategies from tree search to deep reinforcement learning. Compete in a 2D grid world collecting power-ups and placing explosives to take your opponent down.
bomberlandLandingPage.openChallenge: Bomberland is an unsolved environment requiring real-time decision-making, and navigating both adversarial and cooperative play. Join a community of professionals and hobbyists exploring new technologies to solve a new challenge for machine learning.
bomberlandLandingPage.simplePlatform: Use any language, framework, or library.

entryTicketPage.title: Entry Ticket
entryTicketPage.description: Purchase your entry ticket for the 2022 Season of Coder One.
entryTicketPage.heading: Your all-in-one season pass
entryTicketPage.coderOneValueProposition: Coder One is a fun way to improve your skills, win prizes and find job opportunities. Join our <1>700+</1> member community by purchasing an Entry Ticket for the season.
entryTicketPage.featureOne: Unlimited submissions and immediate feedback on your agent's performance against other agents
entryTicketPage.featureTwo: Full access to all current and upcoming platform features, both during and after the competition
entryTicketPage.featureThree: Verifiable digital certificate upon completion of the competition
entryTicketPage.featureFour: Discounts and digital giveaways from our partners
entryTicketPage.studentClubNote: <1>Are you currently a university student?</1> You may be eligible for free entry via one of our select university student club partners around Asia-Pacific. <2>Check this page for more details.</2>
entryTicketPage.specialContactNote: If you're experiencing any issues, please contact us at <1>humans@gocoder.one</1>.
entryTicketPage.tip: <1>💡 Tip:</1> you may be able to expense your Entry Ticket with your organization as part of a Learning and Development (L&D) program
